						<span class="comments-link"><a href="http://rumored.com/2018/12/31/end-of-2018/#respond"><span class="dsq-postid" data-dsqidentifier="10015 http://rumored.com/?p=10015"><span class="leave-reply">Leave a reply</span></span></a></span>
			
