						<span class="comments-link"><a href="http://rumored.com/2018/11/27/johns-book-reno-air-kubrick/#respond"><span class="dsq-postid" data-dsqidentifier="10003 http://rumored.com/?p=10003"><span class="leave-reply">Leave a reply</span></span></a></span>
			
